PrecisAmendment to Schedule F to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (Schedule No. 893) permitting clotrimazole and miconazole to be made available without a prescription in topical antifungal preparations for the treatment of vaginal infections, athlete's foot or jock itch.
